WEBVTT

00:01.475 --> 00:03.934
Located on the border of Brazil and Paraguay,...

00:04.020 --> 00:08.181
...the Itaipu Dam is five miles wide and spans the Parana River.

00:08.599 --> 00:10.267
During the course of construction,...

00:10.544 --> 00:15.214
...workers actually had to shift the course of the seventh largest river in the world.

00:15.591 --> 00:18.822
Its main dam stands at 65 stories high.

00:19.141 --> 00:22.589
It took 18 years and 18 billion dollars to build.

00:22.812 --> 00:28.273
It was completed in 1991 and has received more than nine million visitors since.

00:28.585 --> 00:31.457
It has 18 hydroelectric generators...

00:31.619 --> 00:36.278
...and each turbine is hit with 160 tons of water per second.

